text:
What's up guys, it's Jeffrey how's everybody
doing
So last week i uploaded a video
and in it, my dad rudely interrupted me

but you know it's cool i didn't really mind
at first until i started to read the comments

and realized that hundreds of you guys paid
more attention to my dad instead of me

he appeared for barely three seconds and already
some of you were confessing your

love for him and then i read this comment
that that's when I I lost it

plus it has 61 thumbs up... You know what
I feel betrayed

ok first off my dad is already taken and
since when is he even supposed to be a threat

to me and girls listen i'm not saying i'm
jealous or anything but truth
is my dad isn't who you think he is

he might put up this really nice image on
camera but in real life it's all fake

and as a matter of fact he's quite heartless
like I'm his own son and he barely loves me

hey I just wanted to say... You're a pretty
cool dad
Agh, don't touch me

You see? My whole life
he never even once gave me a single compliment

worse part is it feels like he loves Malibu,
our dog, more than he'll ever like me
Up! Good. Turn. Down. Down, down.
Pew! Good doggy, good doggy! Good good girl!

That's disgusting. She's not even from the same
bloodline. Pfff, whatever
oh and that's not all

My dad is also a very lazy person. He spends
most of his time watching these asian dramas

on the couch and he even falls asleep watching
them

yeah and also he's not even close to being
as manly as you think

like when we asked to have with simple things
like gardening he gets all grumpy
because he's too afraid to get dirty

ok that's the chair from our living room and is he wearing
mom's hat? my god
Ughhh Oh my god...
What was he wearing?

oh and speaking of clothes I don't really
understand his sense of style
in fact I think it's pretty terrible

ok so my dad wants me to give him my opinion
on shoes he wants to buy
Wait are you serious?

what's wrong with them?
what are those
But...
What ARE THOSE?

and contrary to what most people would believe
in a real life
my dad isn't even that funny

like one thing you think he's really funny
or cool
is to imitate how he thinks I act around my friends
Yo what's GUCCI man
You already know who it is! Ha ha ha!
Pfff, I don't act like that
anyways I'm telling you
I'm way cooler than him

I hope this clears up some confusion that
some of the girls were having

oh it feels so good to just finally let it
out

I mean thank you all so much for watching
I'll see you all very soon

This is JeffreyFever and
I'm pressing the record button
now! Peace!

Are you talking about me? No!
Dad! Stop trying to be on camera!
Why?
Stop!
Hi!
[Camera falls]
GUGH
